                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 3
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per minute</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The howling terror launches a torrent of molten metal in a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 100 feet. The burst deals @Damage[3d6[bludgeoning]|options:area-damage] damage and @Damage[2d6[fire]|options:area-damage] damage with a Basic @Check[reflex|dc:21] save. Creatures that enter the area or start their turn there take @Damage[1[fire]|options:area-damage] damage until the metal cools after 5 rounds.</p>"
                },
